Package org.semanticweb.kaon2.api.logic

Interface Summary
ClassicalNegation Represents the classical negation of a formula.
Conjunction A formula that represents the conjunction of other formulae.
Constant Represents a constant in a literal.
DefaultNegation Represents the default negation (negation-as-failure) of a formula.
Disjunction A formula that represents the disjunction of other formulae.
Equivalence Represents an equivalence formula.
Exists Implements an existentially quantified formula.
FactFormula This is a tagging interface that identifies formulae that represent facts.
Forall Implements a universally quantified formula.
Formula Represents a FOL formula.
FunctionalTerm Represents an application of a function symbol to terms.
Implication Represents an implication formula.
Literal Represents a literal in the rule.
Predicate Represents a predicate in the program.
PredicateSymbol Represents a predicate in a program which does not come from an OWL knowledge base.
QueryDefinition Rerepsents a definition of a query.
Rule Represents a rule in the program.
Term Represents a term of a literal.
Variable Represents a variable in a literal.
 

Class Summary
Rule.SubsumptionResult Returns the result of a subsumption check.
 

Enum Summary
Rule.SubsumptionType The enumeration of the types of subsumption relationships.
